{"title":"蒋区学生大罢课","authors":["金钢声"],"dates":[{"year":1947,"month":1,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋区学生大罢课"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金钢声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老乡们,快快传："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国鬼子兵欺侮咱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各地学生起来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罢课游行闹翻天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圣诞节，前一天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个美军撒了欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等在电影院门口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一心要把中国女人玩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姓沈的，女学生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独自离开电影院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个野兽赶上去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一左一右把她拦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉到操场树林里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轮流替换来强奸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人见到不敢管，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报告警察也不动弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国宪兵请来到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个抓到一个窜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可怜那十七岁的沈姓女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昏迷不醒泪涟涟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若问他住啥学校？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京大学先修班；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事情出在哪一地？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北平城里靠近东单。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些美兵哪里来？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老蒋磕头把他搬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老乡们，想想看："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎不叫人怒冲天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎不叫人怒冲天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北平学生怒冲冲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决定示威大游行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋家政府心惊怕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"命令校长压学生；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学生不管这一套，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腊月三十把课停。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三万多人排大队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吼声震动北平城。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫老乡，你听听，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口号喊得多么凶："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“美军滚出中国去！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“行凶的兽兵要严惩！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三万条臂膀一齐挥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四人一排一阵风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小传单，大标语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贴到美军总部大门中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一辆美军吉普街上过，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马上贴成个花纸灯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电报打到美国去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不撤美兵那不中！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从北平、到天津，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海、杭州到南京。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大学生，中学生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男学生，女学生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一齐起来、抗议、示威、游行把课停。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"包围天津市政府，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过年的宴席摆不成；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海学生提得好："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“抵制美货”要实行；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南京包围美使馆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书面质问斯徒雷登。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老蒋一见心害怕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下令不准把报登。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"禁止游行不准闹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像强奸他很欢迎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又派特务学生狗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说那女生不正经。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大学教授也怒恼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主张开除狗学生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九四七元旦起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学生运动热烘烘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先锋总是学生打，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟后起来各阶层，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰轰烈烈来响应，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一齐要赶走美国兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反对老蒋把国卖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独裁的天下他坐不成。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独裁的天下他坐不成。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}